<p>Related: <a href="https://www.foodnetwork.ca/article/canadian-muslim-women-ramadan-celebrations/">Here’s How Canadian Muslim Women Celebrated Ramadan</a></p>


</div><div class="gallery"><div class="ad-wrapper gallery-ad-1"><span class="ad-label">ADVERTISEMENT</span><div class="ad-slot gallery-ad-1-wrapper adunitContainer"><div class="adBox" id="gallery-ad-1"></div></div></div><div class="gallery-slide"><a class="gallery-slide-image-link" aria-label="Link to Easy Puff Pastry Potato Samosas" target="_blank" href="https://www.foodnetwork.ca/recipe/puff-pastry-potato-samosas/"><div class="gallery-slide-image"><div class="corus-image-wrapper" style="max-width:1280px;margin:auto"><img alt="puff pastry samosas on a serving platter" loading="lazy" width="1280" height="853" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="gallery-slide-image-file" style="color:transparent;width:100%;height:auto" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcSet="https://api.vip.foodnetwork.ca/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/puff-pastry-samosas-feat.jpg?w=640&amp;quality=75 640w, https://api.vip.foodnetwork.ca/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/puff-pastry-samosas-feat.jpg?w=704&amp;quality=75 704w, https://api.vip.foodnetwork.ca/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/puff-pastry-samosas-feat.jpg?w=750&amp;quality=75 750w, https://api.vip.foodnetwork.ca/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/puff-pastry-samosas-feat.jpg?w=828&amp;quality=75 828w, https://api.vip.foodnetwork.ca/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/puff-pastry-samosas-feat.jpg?w=856&amp;quality=75 856w, https://api.vip.foodnetwork.ca/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/puff-pastry-samosas-feat.jpg?w=1080&amp;quality=75 1080w, https://api.vip.foodnetwork.ca/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/puff-pastry-samosas-feat.jpg?w=1200&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://api.vip.foodnetwork.ca/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/puff-pastry-samosas-feat.jpg?w=1920&amp;quality=75 1920w, https://api.vip.foodnetwork.ca/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/puff-pastry-samosas-feat.jpg?w=2048&amp;quality=75 2048w, https://api.vip.foodnetwork.ca/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/puff-pastry-samosas-feat.jpg?w=3840&amp;quality=75 3840w" src="https://api.vip.foodnetwork.ca/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/puff-pastry-samosas-feat.jpg?w=3840&amp;quality=75"/></div></div></a><div class="gallery-slide-image-caption"> </div><div class="gallery-slide-number"><span class="gallery-slide-number-current">1</span>/<span class="gallery-slide-number-total">10</span></div><h2 class="gallery-slide-title">Easy Puff Pastry Potato Samosas</h2><div class="gallery-slide-description"><p>We start off our list with a twist on the classic samosa, a quintessential Ramadan Iftar item. Folding and frying samosas can be time consuming, so instead, make these easy puff pastry samosas ahead of time and freeze to enjoy throughout the month. Filled with a delicious potato filling and baked in the oven, they’re a breeze to make and absolutely delicious!</p>


</div><a class="gallery-slide-cta button-primary" target="_blank" href="https://www.foodnetwork.ca/recipe/puff-pastry-potato-samosas/">Get the recipe</a></div><div class="gallery-slide"><a class="gallery-slide-image-link" aria-label="Link to Classic Chinese Spring Rolls" target="_blank" href="https://www.foodnetwork.ca/recipe/classic-chinese-spring-rolls/"><div class="gallery-slide-image"><div class="corus-image-wrapper" style="max-width:1280px;margin:auto"><img alt="Chinese spring rolls on a plate" loading="lazy" width="1280" height="853" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="gallery-slide-image-file" style="color:transparent;width:100%;height:auto" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcSet="https://api.vip.foodnetwork.ca/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/spring-rolls-feat4.jpg?w=640&amp;quality=75 640w, https://api.vip.foodnetwork.ca/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/spring-rolls-feat4.jpg?w=704&amp;quality=75 704w, https://api.vip.foodnetwork.ca/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/spring-rolls-feat4.jpg?w=750&amp;quality=75 750w, https://api.vip.foodnetwork.ca/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/spring-rolls-feat4.jpg?w=828&amp;quality=75 828w, https://api.vip.foodnetwork.ca/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/spring-rolls-feat4.jpg?w=856&amp;quality=75 856w, https://api.vip.foodnetwork.ca/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/spring-rolls-feat4.jpg?w=1080&amp;quality=75 1080w, https://api.vip.foodnetwork.ca/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/spring-rolls-feat4.jpg?w=1200&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://api.vip.foodnetwork.ca/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/spring-rolls-feat4.jpg?w=1920&amp;quality=75 1920w, https://api.vip.foodnetwork.ca/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/spring-rolls-feat4.jpg?w=2048&amp;quality=75 2048w, https://api.vip.foodnetwork.ca/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/spring-rolls-feat4.jpg?w=3840&amp;quality=75 3840w" src="https://api.vip.foodnetwork.ca/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/spring-rolls-feat4.jpg?w=3840&amp;quality=75"/></div></div></a><div class="gallery-slide-image-caption"> </div><div class="gallery-slide-number"><span class="gallery-slide-number-current">2</span>/<span class="gallery-slide-number-total">10</span></div><h2 class="gallery-slide-title">Classic Chinese Spring Rolls</h2><div class="gallery-slide-description"><p>Like samosas, one cannot resist crispy savoury spring rolls after a long day of fasting. Try these authentic Chinese spring rolls, a special heirloom recipe handed down by <a href="https://www.foodnetwork.ca/profile/lara-buchar/">Lara Buchar</a>’s grandmother herself. Tip: make and freeze more than you think you’ll need, they disappear quick!</p>
<p>Related: <a href="https://www.foodnetwork.ca/recipe/instant-pot-chicken-congee/">Easiest Ever Instant Pot Chicken Congee</a></p>


</div><a class="gallery-slide-cta button-primary" target="_blank" href="https://www.foodnetwork.ca/recipe/classic-chinese-spring-rolls/">Get the recipe</a></div><div class="gallery-slide"><a class="gallery-slide-image-link" aria-label="Link to Arabic Lentil Soup" target="_blank" href="https://www.foodnetwork.ca/recipe/arabic-lentil-soup-ramadan/"><div class="gallery-slide-image"><div class="corus-image-wrapper" style="max-width:1280px;margin:auto"><img alt="Classic Arabic lentil soup" loading="lazy" width="1280" height="853" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="gallery-slide-image-file" style="color:transparent;width:100%;height:auto" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcSet="https://api.vip.foodnetwork.ca/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/lentil-soup-feat.jpg?w=640&amp;quality=75 640w, https://api.vip.foodnetwork.ca/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/lentil-soup-feat.jpg?w=704&amp;quality=75 704w, https://api.vip.foodnetwork.ca/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/lentil-soup-feat.jpg?w=750&amp;quality=75 750w, https://api.vip.foodnetwork.ca/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/lentil-soup-feat.jpg?w=828&amp;quality=75 828w, https://api.vip.foodnetwork.ca/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/lentil-soup-feat.jpg?w=856&amp;quality=75 856w, https://api.vip.foodnetwork.ca/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/lentil-soup-feat.jpg?w=1080&amp;quality=75 1080w, https://api.vip.foodnetwork.ca/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/lentil-soup-feat.jpg?w=1200&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://api.vip.foodnetwork.ca/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/lentil-soup-feat.jpg?w=1920&amp;quality=75 1920w, https://api.vip.foodnetwork.ca/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/lentil-soup-feat.jpg?w=2048&amp;quality=75 2048w, https://api.vip.foodnetwork.ca/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/lentil-soup-feat.jpg?w=3840&amp;quality=75 3840w" src="https://api.vip.foodnetwork.ca/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/lentil-soup-feat.jpg?w=3840&amp;quality=75"/></div></div></a><div class="gallery-slide-image-caption"> </div><div class="gallery-slide-number"><span class="gallery-slide-number-current">3</span>/<span class="gallery-slide-number-total">10</span></div><h2 class="gallery-slide-title">Arabic Lentil Soup</h2><div class="gallery-slide-description"><p>In many Arab cultures, the first meal after breaking fast is <a href="https://www.foodnetwork.ca/recipe/persian-lentil-soup-adasi/">a hearty and warming lentil soup</a>. Nourishing and comforting, this soup will prepare your stomach for the meal to come while providing key nutrients like protein, iron and healthy carbohydrates. Make ahead, <a href="https://www.foodnetwork.ca/tag/freezer-friendly/">freeze in batches</a>, and simply reheat on the stove for a delicious, healthy Iftar option.</p>


